snippet: Graeme McDowell of Northern Ireland and Richard Sterne of South Africa shared a one-stroke lead after three rounds of the French Open in Saint-Quentin-en-Yvelines.
abstract: Graeme McDowell and Richard Sterne share third-round lead at French Open golf tournament; other golf new noted.

headline.main: McDowell Shares Lead in French Open
